{"article_id":"wwEEdZ7xmO4SSqAU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The police chief said","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"that Wilson was originally investigating a 'sick call . '","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Officer ID 'd in Brown shooting","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"Ferguson Police Chief Thomas Jackson announced Friday morning","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that the officer","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"who fatally shot unarmed 18-year-old Michael Brown","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"is Darren Wilson .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"At a news conference in Ferguson , Missouri , Jackson said","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Wilson has been a Ferguson police officer for six years .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"He has had no disciplinary action taken against him prior to the incident","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"and has been treated for injuries","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"following the altercation ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"Jackson said .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"The police chief said","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that Wilson was originally investigating a \" sick call \" before noon on Saturday ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"and then responded to a reported robbery at a nearby Ferguson convenience store ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"of which Brown allegedly was a suspect .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"After his announcement , Jackson did not take questions","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"or specify Wilson ' s age .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Jackson did release several police reports and documents","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"regarding the robbery and shooting of Brown ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"The Associated Press reported .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"The reports ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"according to the AP ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Brown and his friend were believed to be two individuals","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"who were suspected of taking a box of cigars from a Ferguson store earlier Saturday , prior to Brown ' s death .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Wilson was sent to investigate the robbery ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"before encountering Brown shortly after .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"The officer","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"who shot and killed Brown","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"did not know","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that Brown was a suspect in the robbery at the time ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Jackson said at a later press conference on Friday .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Before Jackson appeared at the press conference ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"the officer was \" devastated \" by the shooting incident ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"according to a CNN report .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"\" This is his community .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"He never wanted any of this to happen , \"","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"the police chief said ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"according to the report .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"The announcement comes after nearly a weeklong wait for the release of the officer ' s name .","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"The department said","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"that the delay was intended to protect the officer ' s safety ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"but the slow response angered many members of the Ferguson community .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"After the announcement , John Gaskin , a member of the St. Louis County NAACP , said","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"the release of the officer ' s name was a \" small step \" toward justice for Brown and his family .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"\" It ' s a small step ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"but it ' s definitely a step in the direction of justice , \"","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"he said on MSNBC .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"\" [ The Ferguson Police Department ] owed the family this information .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"They owed the people of this community this information .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"To know","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"who this man is on the ground ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"so now the NAACP can do our due diligence","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and begin speaking with the police department on who this officer was .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"I know","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"they say","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"his record was fairly clean ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"but we ' d like to speak with some of the people here on the ground","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"to find out what their reaction is","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and had they had any run-ins with this officer . \"","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Gaskin added","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"that he was \" nervous \" about the possibility","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that Brown may have been the subject of racial profiling ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"given Jackson ' s reference to the convenience store robbery in his press conference .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Earlier Friday morning , Missouri Gov . Jay Nixon said","depth":4},{"id":68,"text":"he was glad about the anticipated move by law enforcement officials .","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"\" I think","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"it ' s great news today","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"that after a great deal of prodding , that they ' re going to be releasing the name of the officer , \"","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"Nixon told MSNBC ' s \" Morning Joe \" .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":145,"left":75,"right":144,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":144,"left":138,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":113,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":90,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":84,"right":89,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":78,"right":8